{"name":"Brimgar","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Patron, Devil","alignment":"Lawful Evil","hitDice":"50","armorName":"natural armor","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":10,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"30","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"425 (50d8 + 200)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"14","conPoints":"18","intPoints":"10","wisPoints":"22","chaPoints":"22","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"60","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"15","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"Brimgar can take 3 legendary actions.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Legendary Resistance (3/day)","desc":"If [MON] fails a saving throw, he can choose to succeed instead."},{"name":"Magic Resistance","desc":"[MON] has advantage on saving throws against magical effects."},{"name":"Panoply of Agathys","desc":"[MON] has a 40HP Armor of Agathys that deals 40 cold damage."},{"name":"Soul Tithes","desc":"When a creature has Stacks of Control, [MON] may control their:\n\n1 Stack - Reaction\n2 Stacks - Bonus Action\n3 Stacks - Movement\n4 Stacks - Action\n\n> The stacks decrease by 1 at the end of a creature's turn."}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes three weapon attacks."},{"name":"Lex Dominus","desc":"[MON] slashes with a fiendish sword that magically compels the soul to obey [MON]. [STR ATK + 1] to hit. _Hit:_ [STR 2D12 + 1] slashing damage. The target must make a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Wisdom save or gain a Stack of Control."},{"name":"Firestorm","desc":"[MON] unleashes eight **DC [CHA SAVE]** fireballs. The fireballs cannot overlap."},{"name":"Cataclysmic Wrath","desc":"[MON] brings down a pillar of fire that incinerates everything within a 60ft. radius. All creatures within the pillar takes [20d6] fire damage, or halved if they succeed a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Dex Save."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Heatwave","desc":"[MON] unleashes a heat wave that knocks all creatures a 5ft. radius prone if they fail a **DC [CHA SAVE + 1]** Con Save."},{"name":"Soulbind","desc":"A creature within a 90ft. radius must make a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Charisma Save or gain 4 stacks of control."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[{"name":"Flyby","desc":"[MON] flies up to 30ft."},{"name":"Slash","desc":"[MON] makes an attack with the Lex Domninus."},{"name":"Dominate Person (2 legendary actions)","desc":"[MON] casts a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Dominate Person."}],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"wis","order":4}],"skills":[{"name":"deception","stat":"cha"},{"name":"insight","stat":"wis"},{"name":"intimidation","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[{"name":"fire","note":" (Immune)","type":"i"}],"specialdamage":[{"name":"bludgeoning, piercing, and slashing from nonmagical attacks","note":" (Resistant)","type":"r"}],"conditions":[{"name":"charmed"}],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":4,"damage":[]}